          "Substitute the values into the formula.",
          "Perform the arithmetic calculation.",
          "Express the final result in square units."
        ],
        "derivation": "\\text{Area} = \\frac{1}{2} |1(6 - (-5)) + (-4)(-5 - (-1)) + (-3)(-1 - 6)| \\\\ = \\frac{1}{2} |1(11) + (-4)(-4) + (-3)(-7)| \\\\ = \\frac{1}{2} |11 + 16 + 21| \\\\ = \\frac{1}{2} |48| = 24 \\text{ Sq. units}"
